import Button from '@mui/material/Button';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';

export default function NavBar() {

                        padding: '12px 24px',
                        minWidth: '120px',
                        color: '#000000',
                    }}
                    variant="text"
                    href="/home"
                >
                    Healthy ðŸ˜‹n the Hill

                    }}

                >

                </Button>
                <Button
                    style={{

                        padding: '12px 24px',
                        minWidth: '120px'
                    }}
                    variant="text"

                >
                    Log Out

            </Box>
            <Divider />
        </Box>

    );
}
